    "description": {
      "value": "<h2><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">JUST STOP<br /></span></span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">At 19</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size: 6pt;\">th </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">level, you can increase one ability score of your choice by 2, or you can increase two ability scores of your choice by 1. You can&rsquo;t increase an ability score above 20 using this feature except for your primary born leader ability, which has a maximum value of 22. Additionally, you are able to take a moment to focus and gather your wits, as well as the wits of your allies. Use an action, and you and all allies able to communicate with you gain the benefit of a short rest. This takes no time other than the action on your turn. After you use this ability, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest.</span> </span></p>",
